<script>
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
    let slideInterval;

    // Function to navigate to a specific slide
    function navigateToSlide(slideIndex) {
      // Find the Webflow slider element
      const slider = document.querySelector('.w-slider');
      // Trigger the click event on the corresponding nav dot
      const navDots = slider.querySelectorAll('.w-slider-nav .w-slider-dot');
      if (navDots[slideIndex]) {
        navDots[slideIndex].click();
      }
      // Reset the timer
      resetSlideInterval();
    }

    // Function to navigate to the next slide
    function goToNextSlide() {
      const slider = document.querySelector('.w-slider');
      const nextButton = slider.querySelector('.w-slider-arrow-right');
      if (nextButton) {
        nextButton.click();
      }
    }

    // Function to reset the slide interval
    function resetSlideInterval() {
      clearInterval(slideInterval);
      slideInterval = setInterval(goToNextSlide, 8000);
    }

    // Add event listeners to buttons with the data-slide-index attribute
    const buttons = document.querySelectorAll('[data-slide-index]');
    buttons.forEach(button => {
      button.addEventListener('click', function() {
        const slideIndex = parseInt(button.getAttribute('data-slide-index'), 10);
        navigateToSlide(slideIndex);
      });
    });

    // Initialize the slide interval
    resetSlideInterval();
  });
</script>
